{"title":"四位老人","authors":["西中扬"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":6,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"四位老人\t西中扬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈子摇橹使船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走不尽波涛风险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨里飘洋过海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪儿是安全港湾？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四位年近七十岁的老人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今变成了鹤发童颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通红的大字报捧给公社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们决心要修一只红船！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝霞里扬起板斧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月下敞开衣衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社门前抖擞精神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老英雄不减当年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叮咚咚敲醒晨鸡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噹啷啷震动山峦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船头上描龙绘凤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船舷上刻下锦绣河山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是给公社置点家当，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社的财富成千上万！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是向党报答恩情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党的恩情重如泰山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是修一艘红色船只，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻下祖辈的心愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟随着公社破浪远航，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扯起那不落的风帆！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}